cdata.name: Bittwatt
cdata.desc:
Bittwattis adecentralizedmatchmaking platformthat aims to become a digital currency solution for energy supply, billing and balancing with P2P settlements.The system works by analyzing smart contracts that link production and demand data with energy wallets available on the network. Bittwattincludes regulatory information shared between energy suppliers, grid operators and consumers. The idea is to enable the exchange of energy for cryptocurrencies.

BWT is an Ethereum-based token developed by the Bittwatt and acts as a medium of exchange within the platform.
